      <title>罢工僵局两周后波音重返薪资谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/boeing-returns-to-wage-talks-after-two-weeks-of-strike-stalemate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两周前，波音公司试图通过直接向工人提出要约的大胆举动来结束罢工，但未能成功，现在，这家飞机制造商及其最大的工会再次尝试采用更为传统的协商和穿梭外交模式来结束僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/boeing-returns-to-wage-talks-after-two-weeks-of-strike-stalemate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>周二中国经济部门简报会有何展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/what-to-expect-from-china-economic-agency-s-briefing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗全球市场新兴市场经济主管 Johanna Chua 讨论了她预计中国国家发展和改革委员会周二召开新闻发布会时会透露哪些内容。在中国高层领导人表示希望结束经济增长放缓后，经济学家和交易员正在密切关注进一步的政策措施。Chua 在“彭博：中国秀”上发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/what-to-expect-from-china-economic-agency-s-briefing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铁矿石价格因预期中国将出台更多刺激措施而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/iron-ore-pushes-higher-on-hopes-more-china-stimulus-is-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[因市场猜测中国最高经济规划者将在周二上午的新闻发布会上推出更多刺激措施，铁矿石价格在连续两周大幅上涨之后也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/iron-ore-pushes-higher-on-hopes-more-china-stimulus-is-coming</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行称已准备好在卢比暴跌后采取干预措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bank-indonesia-says-it-s-ready-to-intervene-after-rupiah-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行表示，已准备好介入以支持印尼盾，印尼盾目前正处于 2023 年以来最长的连续下跌期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bank-indonesia-says-it-s-ready-to-intervene-after-rupiah-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 03:38:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国奥拉诺公司在蒙古铀矿开发方面取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/france-s-orano-sees-progress-developing-uranium-mine-in-mongolia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国有矿业公司 Orano SA 表示，该公司正在蒙古开发一个长期拖延、耗资数十亿美元的铀矿项目，预计将于 2030 年开始生产核燃料。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/france-s-orano-sees-progress-developing-uranium-mine-in-mongolia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 02:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元疲软推动日本股市上涨；银行股收益率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/japanese-stocks-set-to-jump-after-us-jobs-data-spur-yen-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于就业报告强于预期，凸显了美国经济的韧性，日元下跌，日本股市上涨。随着日本基准债券收益率上升，东京金融股上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/japanese-stocks-set-to-jump-after-us-jobs-data-spur-yen-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业报告提振市场人气，亚洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[强于预期的美国就业数据凸显了全球最大经济体的健康状况并提振了投资者的乐观情绪，亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注以色列对伊朗袭击的回应，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周油价开盘走低，市场等待观察以色列是否会对上周的导弹袭击对伊朗进行报复，美国总统乔·拜登也不鼓励对伊朗油田进行袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>力拓拟以 33 亿美元收购 Arcadium Litium 公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/rio-tinto-confirms-it-s-made-an-approach-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-m1y5cwtw</link>
      <description><![CDATA[双方周一表示，力拓集团 (Rio Tinto Group) 已对 Arcadium Lithium Plc 发出收购要约，确认了这一最新收购提议。目前，该行业正将注意力重新转向增长，各大矿业公司都在竞相增加对能源过渡金属的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/rio-tinto-confirms-it-s-made-an-approach-to-buy-arcadium-lithium-m1y5cwtw</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
